{
  "video_id": "ezVk1ahRF78",
  "title": "Religions and babies | Hans Rosling",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Timothy Covell Reviewer: Morton Bast"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15617.0,
      "end_time": 19482.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to talk about religion."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19482.0,
      "end_time": 24734.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s a broad and very delicate subject,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24734.0,
      "end_time": 26405.0,
      "text": "so I have to limit myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26405.0,
      "end_time": 28885.0,
      "text": "And therefore I will limit myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28885.0,
      "end_time": 33294.0,
      "text": "to only talk about the links between religion and sexuality."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33294.0,
      "end_time": 34860.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34860.0,
      "end_time": 37420.0,
      "text": "This is a very serious talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37420.0,
      "end_time": 41515.0,
      "text": "So I will talk of what I remember as the most wonderful."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 41515.0,
      "end_time": 43860.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s when the young couple whisper,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43860.0,
      "end_time": 47320.0,
      "text": "\"Tonight we are going to make a baby.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47320.0,
      "end_time": 52367.0,
      "text": "My talk will be about the impact of religions"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52368.0,
      "end_time": 56537.0,
      "text": "on the number of babies per woman."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 56537.0,
      "end_time": 58202.0,
      "text": "This is indeed important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 58202.0,
      "end_time": 59732.0,
      "text": "because everyone understands"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 59732.0,
      "end_time": 62130.0,
      "text": "that there is some sort of limit"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 62140.0,
      "end_time": 65242.0,
      "text": "on how many people we can be on this planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 65242.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67189.0,
      "text": "And there are some people"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 67189.0,
      "end_time": 70607.0,
      "text": "who say that the world population is growing like this --"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 70608.0,
      "end_time": 72415.0,
      "text": "three billion in 1960,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 72415.0,
      "end_time": 75540.0,
      "text": "seven billion just last year --"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 75540.0,
      "end_time": 76600.0,
      "text": "and it will continue to grow"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 76600.0,
      "end_time": 80380.0,
      "text": "because there are religions that stop women from having few babies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 80380.0,
      "end_time": 82783.0,
      "text": "and it may continue like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 82783.0,
      "end_time": 86685.0,
      "text": "To what extent are these people right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 86685.0,
      "end_time": 91565.0,
      "text": "When I was born there was less than one billion children in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 91565.0,
      "end_time": 95740.0,
      "text": "and today, 2000, there&#39;s almost two billion."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 95740.0,
      "end_time": 97442.0,
      "text": "What has happened since,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 97442.0,
      "end_time": 100136.0,
      "text": "and what do the experts predict will happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 100137.0,
      "end_time": 102620.0,
      "text": "with the number of children during this century?"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 102620.0,
      "end_time": 105238.0,
      "text": "This is a quiz. What do you think?"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 105238.0,
      "end_time": 109140.0,
      "text": "Do you think it will decrease to one billion?"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 109140.0,
      "end_time": 112968.0,
      "text": "Will it remain the same and be two billion by the end of the century?"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 112968.0,
      "end_time": 116685.0,
      "text": "Will the number of children increase each year up to 15 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 116685.0,
      "end_time": 119189.0,
      "text": "or will it continue in the same fast rate"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 119189.0,
      "end_time": 121678.0,
      "text": "and be four billion children up there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 121678.0,
      "end_time": 125103.0,
      "text": "I will tell you by the end of my speech."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 125103.0,
      "end_time": 130125.0,
      "text": "But now, what does religion have to do with it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 130125.0,
      "end_time": 132457.0,
      "text": "When you want to classify religion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 132457.0,
      "end_time": 133988.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s more difficult than you think."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 133988.0,
      "end_time": 137192.0,
      "text": "You go to Wikipedia and the first map you find is this."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 137192.0,
      "end_time": 142725.0,
      "text": "It divides the world into Abrahamic religions and Eastern religion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 142725.0,
      "end_time": 144497.0,
      "text": "but that&#39;s not detailed enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 144497.0,
      "end_time": 148306.0,
      "text": "So we went on and we looked in Wikipedia, we found this map."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 148306.0,
      "end_time": 152952.0,
      "text": "But that subdivides Christianity, Islam and Buddhism"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 152952.0,
      "end_time": 154555.0,
      "text": "into many subgroups,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 154555.0,
      "end_time": 156600.0,
      "text": "which was too detailed."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 156600.0,
      "end_time": 159478.0,
      "text": "Therefore at Gapminder we made our own map,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 159478.0,
      "end_time": 161851.0,
      "text": "and it looks like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 161851.0,
      "end_time": 165254.0,
      "text": "Each country&#39;s a bubble."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 165254.0,
      "end_time": 168678.0,
      "text": "The size is the population -- big China, big India here."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 168678.0,
      "end_time": 172792.0,
      "text": "And the color now is the majority religion."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 172792.0,
      "end_time": 176230.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the religion where more than 50 percent of the people"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 176230.0,
      "end_time": 177278.0,
      "text": "say that they belong."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 177278.0,
      "end_time": 181995.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s Eastern religion in India and China and neighboring Asian countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 181995.0,
      "end_time": 183968.0,
      "text": "Islam is the majority religion"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 183968.0,
      "end_time": 187743.0,
      "text": "all the way from the Atlantic Ocean across the Middle East,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 187743.0,
      "end_time": 190230.0,
      "text": "Southern Europe and through Asia"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 190230.0,
      "end_time": 192260.0,
      "text": "all the way to Indonesia."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 192260.0,
      "end_time": 195177.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s where we find Islamic majority."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 195177.0,
      "end_time": 199980.0,
      "text": "And Christian majority religions, we see in these countries. They are blue."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 199980.0,
      "end_time": 204500.0,
      "text": "And that is most countries in America and Europe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 204500.0,
      "end_time": 207674.0,
      "text": "many countries in Africa and a few in Asia."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 207675.0,
      "end_time": 210355.0,
      "text": "The white here are countries which cannot be classified,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 210355.0,
      "end_time": 212980.0,
      "text": "because one religion does not reach 50 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 212980.0,
      "end_time": 216337.0,
      "text": "or there is doubt about the data or there&#39;s some other reason."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 216337.0,
      "end_time": 218960.0,
      "text": "So we were careful with that."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 218970.0,
      "end_time": 221955.0,
      "text": "So bear with our simplicity now when I take you over to this shot."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 221955.0,
      "end_time": 223968.0,
      "text": "This is in 1960."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 223968.0,
      "end_time": 227500.0,
      "text": "And now I show the number of babies per woman here:"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 227500.0,
      "end_time": 230586.0,
      "text": "two, four or six --"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 230586.0,
      "end_time": 232777.0,
      "text": "many babies, few babies."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 232777.0,
      "end_time": 235958.0,
      "text": "And here the income per person in comparable dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 235958.0,
      "end_time": 239555.0,
      "text": "The reason for that is that many people say you have to get rich first"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 239555.0,
      "end_time": 241225.0,
      "text": "before you get few babies."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 241225.0,
      "end_time": 244857.0,
      "text": "So low income here, high income there."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 244857.0,
      "end_time": 246495.0,
      "text": "And indeed in 1960,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 246495.0,
      "end_time": 249232.0,
      "text": "you had to be a rich Christian to have few babies."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 249232.0,
      "end_time": 251506.0,
      "text": "The exception was Japan."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 251506.0,
      "end_time": 254743.0,
      "text": "Japan here was regarded as an exception."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 254743.0,
      "end_time": 256771.0,
      "text": "Otherwise it was only Christian countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 256771.00000000003,
      "end_time": 258980.00000000003,
      "text": "But there was also many Christian countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 258980.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261552.00000000003,
      "text": "that had six to seven babies per woman."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 261552.00000000003,
      "end_time": 267290.0,
      "text": "But they were in Latin America or they were in Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 267290.0,
      "end_time": 271202.0,
      "text": "And countries with Islam as the majority religion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 271202.0,
      "end_time": 275832.0,
      "text": "all of them almost had six to seven children per woman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 275832.0,
      "end_time": 278257.0,
      "text": "irregardless of the income level."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 278257.0,
      "end_time": 282500.0,
      "text": "And all the Eastern religions except Japan had the same level."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 282500.0,
      "end_time": 284420.0,
      "text": "Now let&#39;s see what has happened in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 284420.0,
      "end_time": 286340.0,
      "text": "I start the world, and here we go."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 286340.0,
      "end_time": 289558.0,
      "text": "Now 1962 -- can you see they&#39;re getting a little richer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 289558.0,
      "end_time": 292232.0,
      "text": "but the number of babies per woman is falling?"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 292232.0,
      "end_time": 294405.0,
      "text": "Look at China. They&#39;re falling fairly fast."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 294405.0,
      "end_time": 299167.0,
      "text": "And all of the Muslim majority countries across the income are coming down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 299168.0,
      "end_time": 304131.0,
      "text": "as do the Christian majority countries in the middle income range."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 304131.0,
      "end_time": 306659.0,
      "text": "And when we enter into this century,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 306660.0,
      "end_time": 310200.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll find more than half of mankind down here."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 310200.0,
      "end_time": 314945.0,
      "text": "And by 2010, we are actually 80 percent of humans"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 314946.0,
      "end_time": 319260.0,
      "text": "who live in countries with about two children per woman."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 319260.0,
      "end_time": 322798.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 322798.0,
      "end_time": 326758.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a quite amazing development which has happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 326758.0,
      "end_time": 328135.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 328135.0,
      "end_time": 331337.0,
      "text": "And these are countries from United States here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 331337.0,
      "end_time": 333498.0,
      "text": "with $40,000 per capita,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 333498.0,
      "end_time": 336445.0,
      "text": "France, Russia, Iran,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 336445.0,
      "end_time": 340970.0,
      "text": "Mexico, Turkey, Algeria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 340970.0,
      "end_time": 342322.0,
      "text": "Indonesia, India"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 342322.0,
      "end_time": 345510.0,
      "text": "and all the way to Bangladesh and Vietnam,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 345510.0,
      "end_time": 349940.0,
      "text": "which has less than five percent of the income per person of the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 349940.0,
      "end_time": 352251.0,
      "text": "and the same amount of babies per woman."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 352251.0,
      "end_time": 355482.0,
      "text": "I can tell you that the data on the number of children per woman"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 355482.0,
      "end_time": 357571.0,
      "text": "is surprisingly good in all countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 357571.0,
      "end_time": 359518.0,
      "text": "We get that from the census data."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 359518.0,
      "end_time": 362910.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not one of these statistics which is very doubtful."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 362911.0,
      "end_time": 364217.0,
      "text": "So what we can conclude"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 364217.0,
      "end_time": 366998.0,
      "text": "is you don&#39;t have to get rich to have few children."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 366998.0,
      "end_time": 369340.0,
      "text": "It has happened across the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 369340.0,
      "end_time": 371917.0,
      "text": "And then when we look at religions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 371918.0,
      "end_time": 374445.0,
      "text": "we can see that the Eastern religions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 374445.0,
      "end_time": 377445.0,
      "text": "indeed there&#39;s not one single country with a majority of that religion"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 377445.0,
      "end_time": 379340.0,
      "text": "that has more than three children."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 379340.0,
      "end_time": 383392.0,
      "text": "Whereas with Islam as a majority religion and Christianity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 383392.0,
      "end_time": 385300.0,
      "text": "you see countries all the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 385300.0,
      "end_time": 387780.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s no major difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 387780.0,
      "end_time": 390580.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s no major difference between these religions."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 390580.0,
      "end_time": 392931.0,
      "text": "There is a difference with income."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 392931.0,
      "end_time": 396859.0,
      "text": "The countries which have many babies per woman here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 396860.0,
      "end_time": 398792.0,
      "text": "they have quite low income."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 398792.0,
      "end_time": 402222.0,
      "text": "Most of them are in sub-Saharan Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 402223.0,
      "end_time": 404885.0,
      "text": "But there are also countries here"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 404885.0,
      "end_time": 409200.0,
      "text": "like Guatemala, like Papua New Guinea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 409200.0,
      "end_time": 411808.0,
      "text": "like Yemen and Afghanistan."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 411808.0,
      "end_time": 415685.0,
      "text": "Many think that Afghanistan here and Congo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 415685.0,
      "end_time": 419135.0,
      "text": "which have suffered severe conflicts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 419135.0,
      "end_time": 421892.0,
      "text": "that they don&#39;t have fast population growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 421892.0,
      "end_time": 423669.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the other way around."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 423669.0,
      "end_time": 427561.0,
      "text": "In the world today, it&#39;s the countries that have the highest mortality rates"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 427562.0,
      "end_time": 429798.0,
      "text": "that have the fastest population growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 429798.0,
      "end_time": 433786.0,
      "text": "Because the death of a child is compensated by one more child."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 433786.0,
      "end_time": 436694.0,
      "text": "These countries have six children per woman."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 436694.0,
      "end_time": 440826.0,
      "text": "They have a sad death rate of one to two children per woman."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 440826.0,
      "end_time": 444645.0,
      "text": "But 30 years from now, Afghanistan will go from 30 million to 60 million."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 444645.0,
      "end_time": 448510.0,
      "text": "Congo will go from 60 to 120."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 448520.0,
      "end_time": 450943.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s where we have the fast population growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 450943.0,
      "end_time": 455288.0,
      "text": "And many think that these countries are stagnant, but they are not."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 455288.0,
      "end_time": 458802.0,
      "text": "Let me compare Senegal, a Muslim dominated country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 458802.0,
      "end_time": 461260.0,
      "text": "with a Christian dominated country, Ghana."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 461260.0,
      "end_time": 464857.0,
      "text": "I take them backwards here to their independence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 464857.0,
      "end_time": 468540.0,
      "text": "when they were up here in the beginning of the 1960s."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 468540.0,
      "end_time": 470638.0,
      "text": "Just look what they have done."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 470638.0,
      "end_time": 472188.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an amazing improvement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 472189.0,
      "end_time": 474426.0,
      "text": "from seven children per woman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 474426.0,
      "end_time": 477491.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ve gone all the way down to between four and five."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 477491.0,
      "end_time": 479780.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a tremendous improvement."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 479780.0,
      "end_time": 480503.0,
      "text": "So what does it take?"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 480503.0,
      "end_time": 484990.0,
      "text": "Well we know quite well what is needed in these countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 484100.0,
      "end_time": 486589.0,
      "text": "You need to have children to survive."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 486589.0,
      "end_time": 489202.0,
      "text": "You need to get out of the deepest poverty"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 489202.0,
      "end_time": 492780.0,
      "text": "so children are not of importance for work in the family."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 492780.0,
      "end_time": 495650.0,
      "text": "You need to have access to some family planning."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 495651.0,
      "end_time": 499983.0,
      "text": "And you need the fourth factor, which perhaps is the most important factor."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 499983.0,
      "end_time": 502891.0,
      "text": "But let me illustrate that fourth factor"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 502891.0,
      "end_time": 504992.0,
      "text": "by looking at Qatar."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 504992.0,
      "end_time": 508792.0,
      "text": "Here we have Qatar today, and there we have Bangladesh today."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 508792.0,
      "end_time": 512429.0,
      "text": "If I take these countries back to the years of their independence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 512429.0,
      "end_time": 515500.0,
      "text": "which is almost the same year -- &#39;71, &#39;72 --"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 515500.0,
      "end_time": 519374.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s a quite amazing development which had happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 519374.0,
      "end_time": 521180.0,
      "text": "Look at Bangladesh and Qatar."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 521179.0,
      "end_time": 524438.0,
      "text": "With so different incomes, it&#39;s almost the same drop"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 524438.0,
      "end_time": 526552.0,
      "text": "in number of babies per woman."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 526552.0,
      "end_time": 528555.0,
      "text": "And what is the reason in Qatar?"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 528555.0,
      "end_time": 530214.0,
      "text": "Well I do as I always do."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 530214.0,
      "end_time": 533986.0,
      "text": "I went to the statistical authority of Qatar, to their webpage --"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 533986.0,
      "end_time": 536117.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a very good webpage. I recommend it --"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 536117.0,
      "end_time": 542608.0,
      "text": "and I looked up -- oh yeah, you can have lots of fun here --"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 542608.0,
      "end_time": 546675.0,
      "text": "and provided free of charge, I found Qatar&#39;s social trends."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 546675.0,
      "end_time": 549200.0,
      "text": "Very interesting. Lots to read."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 549200.0,
      "end_time": 553592.0,
      "text": "I found fertility at birth, and I looked at total fertility rate per woman."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 553592.0,
      "end_time": 557143.0,
      "text": "These are the scholars and experts in the government agency in Qatar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 557143.0,
      "end_time": 559798.0,
      "text": "and they say the most important factors are:"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 559798.0,
      "end_time": 561740.0,
      "text": "\"Increased age at first marriage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 561740.0,
      "end_time": 564765.0,
      "text": "increased educational level of Qatari woman"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 564765.0,
      "end_time": 568780.0,
      "text": "and more women integrated in the labor force.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 568780.0,
      "end_time": 571819.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t agree more. Science couldn&#39;t agree more."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 571820.0,
      "end_time": 574337.0,
      "text": "This is a country that indeed has gone through"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 574337.0,
      "end_time": 577872.0,
      "text": "a very, very interesting modernization."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 577872.0,
      "end_time": 580497.0,
      "text": "So what it is, is these four:"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 580497.0,
      "end_time": 583579.0,
      "text": "Children should survive, children shouldn&#39;t be needed for work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 583580.0,
      "end_time": 586482.0,
      "text": "women should get education and join the labor force"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 586482.0,
      "end_time": 588755.0,
      "text": "and family planning should be accessible."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 588755.0,
      "end_time": 592143.0,
      "text": "Now look again at this."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 592143.0,
      "end_time": 594435.0,
      "text": "The average number of children in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 594435.0,
      "end_time": 597857.0,
      "text": "is like in Colombia -- it&#39;s 2.4 today."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 597857.0,
      "end_time": 600894.0,
      "text": "There are countries up here which are very poor."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 600894.0,
      "end_time": 604845.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s where family planning, better child survival is needed."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 604845.0,
      "end_time": 608632.0,
      "text": "I strongly recommend Melinda Gates&#39; last TEDTalk."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 608632.0,
      "end_time": 614900.0,
      "text": "And here, down, there are many countries which are less than two children per woman."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 614910.0,
      "end_time": 617703.0,
      "text": "So when I go back now to give you the answer of the quiz,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 617703.0,
      "end_time": 619245.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s two."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 619245.0,
      "end_time": 621774.0,
      "text": "We have reached peak child."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 621774.0,
      "end_time": 624663.0,
      "text": "The number of children is not growing any longer in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 624663.0,
      "end_time": 626655.0,
      "text": "We are still debating peak oil,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 626655.0,
      "end_time": 629586.0,
      "text": "but we have definitely reached peak child."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 629586.0,
      "end_time": 632309.0,
      "text": "And the world population will stop growing."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 632309.0,
      "end_time": 634411.0,
      "text": "The United Nations Population Division has said"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 634411.0,
      "end_time": 636851.0,
      "text": "it will stop growing at 10 billion."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 636851.0,
      "end_time": 640891.0,
      "text": "But why do they grow if the number of children doesn&#39;t grow?"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 640891.0,
      "end_time": 643337.0,
      "text": "Well I will show you here."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 643337.0,
      "end_time": 647112.0,
      "text": "I will use these card boxes in which your notebooks came."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 647112.0,
      "end_time": 650945.0,
      "text": "They are quite useful for educational purposes."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 650946.0,
      "end_time": 653854.0,
      "text": "Each card box is one billion people."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 653854.0,
      "end_time": 656522.0,
      "text": "And there are two billion children in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 656522.0,
      "end_time": 663392.0,
      "text": "There are two billion young people between 15 and 30."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 663392.0,
      "end_time": 664862.0,
      "text": "These are rounded numbers."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 664862.0,
      "end_time": 669887.0,
      "text": "Then there is one billion between 30 and 45,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 669888.0,
      "end_time": 673731.0,
      "text": "almost one between 45 and 60."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 673731.0,
      "end_time": 675355.0,
      "text": "And then it&#39;s my box."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 675355.0,
      "end_time": 677380.0,
      "text": "This is me: 60-plus."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 677380.0,
      "end_time": 679542.0,
      "text": "We are here on top."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 679542.0,
      "end_time": 684774.0,
      "text": "So what will happen now is what we call \"the big fill-up.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 684774.0,
      "end_time": 687762.0,
      "text": "You can see that it&#39;s like three billion missing here."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 687762.0,
      "end_time": 692690.0,
      "text": "They are not missing because they&#39;ve died; they were never born."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 692690.0,
      "end_time": 696176.0,
      "text": "Because before 1980, there were much fewer people born"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 696177.0,
      "end_time": 698934.0,
      "text": "than there were during the last 30 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 698934.0,
      "end_time": 702880.0,
      "text": "So what will happen now is quite straightforward."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 702880.0,
      "end_time": 704885.0,
      "text": "The old, sadly, we will die."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 704885.0,
      "end_time": 709540.0,
      "text": "The rest of you, you will grow older and you will get two billion children."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 709540.0,
      "end_time": 712147.0,
      "text": "Then the old will die."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 712148.0,
      "end_time": 716186.0,
      "text": "The rest will grow older and get two billion children."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 716186.0,
      "end_time": 721955.0,
      "text": "And then again the old will die and you will get two billion children."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 721955.0,
      "end_time": 724209.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 724209.0,
      "end_time": 727842.0,
      "text": "This is the great fill-up."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 727842.0,
      "end_time": 730614.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s inevitable."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 730614.0,
      "end_time": 733260.0,
      "text": "And can you see that this increase took place"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 733260.0,
      "end_time": 738630.0,
      "text": "without life getting longer and without adding children?"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 738630.0,
      "end_time": 742968.0,
      "text": "Religion has very little to do with the number of babies per woman."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 742968.0,
      "end_time": 746237.0,
      "text": "All the religions in the world are fully capable"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 746237.0,
      "end_time": 751362.0,
      "text": "to maintain their values and adapt to this new world."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 751362.0,
      "end_time": 756645.0,
      "text": "And we will be just 10 billion in this world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 756645.0,
      "end_time": 760228.0,
      "text": "if the poorest people get out of poverty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 760229.0,
      "end_time": 763402.0,
      "text": "their children survive, they get access to family planning."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 763402.0,
      "end_time": 765302.0,
      "text": "That is needed."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 765302.0,
      "end_time": 771170.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s inevitable that we will be two to three billion more."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 771170.0,
      "end_time": 774229.0,
      "text": "So when you discuss and when you plan"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 774229.0,
      "end_time": 777632.0,
      "text": "for the resources and the energy needed for the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 777632.0,
      "end_time": 779964.0,
      "text": "for human beings on this planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 779965.0,
      "end_time": 782122.0,
      "text": "you have to plan for 10 billion."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 782122.0,
      "end_time": 784271.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 784272.0,
      "end_time": 790358.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}